{"tid":243250,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"奉勸各位巴打唔好買呢隻洗頭水","createTime":"2017-05-14T13:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T13:42:27.000Z","uid":6064,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b01b79e7b9b187467724c34b4c374e64eec79d9","tid":243250,"uid":6064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:42:27.000Z","msg":"唔影牌子廢事話打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但巴打應該估到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/212911_21883baaffacf3b116dfa2467a035757.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F212911_21883baaffacf3b116dfa2467a035757.jpg&h=3f5aeb36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直用開依個牌既洗頭水都相安無事<br />\n咁近排用晒去買枝新<br />\n見到佢有依隻薄荷味<br />\n咁近排天氣熱諗薄荷應該幾舒服就想試下新野<br />\n<br />\n頭先洗頭果陣覺涼涼地都幾好 都無買錯啊<br />\n點知過水先見真章<br />\n洗頭d水流到落龜頭<br />\n仆街 點撚解龜頭咁涼咁乸<br />\n唔通咁後生就廢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來係枝薄荷洗頭水出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經係咁沖水 點知都仲係咁<br />\n無諗過效力連下面都照顧埋 唔慌唔涼<br />\n依家著住條底褲龜頭都仲涼緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日第一日用可能感覺唔準<br />\n聽日將鳩毛當頭髮咁洗試清楚d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}